highlights.text: “RITMO (Bad Boys For Life)” by Black Eyed Peas and J Balvin is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 132 spots at #54.
“Shape of You” by Ed Sheeran has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 146 weeks straight.
“Lose You To Love Me” by Selena Gomez is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #16.
Post Malone has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Circles” is the highest at #3.
